Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:42.24,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(706.875,580)}The Tale of Jiraiya the Gallant\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to this awful rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Joking! I'm just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Master Jiraiya is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He, of all people, wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I bet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never win my bets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rejection makes a man stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}men aren't the ones\N{\i1}who seek happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What a poser...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When he gets back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him keep his cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain... What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That name is an alias that\Ndenotes all six of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that you, Yahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yeah... There was such a guy,\N{\i1}wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NI thought you said Yahiko died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see Yahiko's image in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are his former Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yahiko has been dead\Nfor quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains...is Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it with the wordplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you possess the Rinnegan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about,\NJiraiya-boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my former students\Nis among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Except he didn't use to\Npossess those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You saying there are\Ntwo children of prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that's not it either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I saw the Rinnegan, I convinced\N{\i1}myself that the first one was Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's subtly different\N{\i1}from the Nagato I knew of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, {\i1}upon closer inspection,\N {\i1}none of those six remind me of Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other hand, {\i1}one of them resembles Yahiko...\N {\i1}but possesses Nagato's Rinnegan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you Yahiko...or Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what exactly are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We are Pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We are god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat, Jiraiya-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko! How could you possess\NNagato's eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you knew that,\Nyou could not win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lad! Give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find an opening to defeat them,\Neven if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sense his presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...a barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gastric fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely managed to kill one...\N only after dragging it into my barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My body...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My chakra's agitated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Their identity is a mystery,\Nand they seem to use odd weapons too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no longer mortals...\NThey're something entirely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No one really knows what\Nhe looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And some claim that\Nhe doesn't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That face...\N{\i1}He is unmistakably Yahiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet,\N{\i1}he possesses Nagato's Rinnegan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Yahiko steal them\N{\i1}from Nagato for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are other\N{\i1}Rinnegan bearers as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding such pain enables you\Nto be kind to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes us human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing up? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:08:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That, you need to figure out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many people die here.\NThat pain made me grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case,\Ndoes that mean he is Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is definitely not Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This fellow before us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fought him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a Fuma Clan member I fought right after setting out\N on my journey, following the Great Lord Elder's prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him that scar on his forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's a fellow like him\Ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm even more confused\Nabout this whole Pain mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You will guide that revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The day will come when you will be\Nforced to make a critical choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What must I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make the right choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In my dream, you traveled the world,\Nwriting books.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be...\N{\i1}If this is the prophecy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to go back and face them\Nin order to confirm something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You two please go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not! You will be killed\Nif you go out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They have more eyes,\N and they will not fall for the barrier trap twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not on to us in here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our only chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be killed if I go out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I may be able to learn\Nthe truth about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let this chance slip by, I don't think there's\N anyone else who could get as close to Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our only chance to\Nuncover the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time for the choice\Nthat the Great Lord Elder prophesied!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss and Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,please take the intel on Pain we've gathered so far,\N as well as this corpse and go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And please tell Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma should be enough for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just return by dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup... When we're done here,\NI'll bring Jiraiya-boy on over with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all ninjas that\N{\i1}I've encountered before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've figured out who Pain is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You were too late in figuring it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must let Boss know...about\N{\i1}Pain's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Jiraiya-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good...\N{\i1}My throat has been crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it... At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's useless... I'm passing out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I...going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I failed...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not how you live,\N {\i1}but how you die in {\i1}the ninja world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A ninja's life is not measured\N{\i1}by how they lived
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but rather what they managed\N{\i1}to accomplish before their death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking back, my life has\N{\i1}been nothing but failures...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Continually rejected by Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unable to stop my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And unable to protect either\N{\i1}my student or my mentor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compared to the great deeds {\i1}of the Hokage,\N {\i1}my actions are trifling, {\i1}insignificant things indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could have died like\N{\i1}each of the Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A tale is only good as\N{\i1}its final turn of events, the plot twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Failures must be seen\N{\i1}as mere amusements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are trials, which hone your skills.\N{\i1}I lived believing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in return, I swore I would {\i1}accomplish a deed\N so great {\i1}that it would obliterate all {\i1}of my failures...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'd die a splendid ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least, that's how it\N{\i1}was supposed to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...with my plot twist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My tale, ending like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Great Lord Elder prophesied that\N{\i1}I would guide that revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A person who will make {\i1}a great choice {\i1}that will bring\N either stability {\i1}or destruction to the ninja world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I would defeat Pain, {\i1}stop the Akatsuki,\N {\i1}and save the ninja world {\i1}from destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in the end, I failed in\N{\i1}that choice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How pitiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that this will be the twist to\N{\i1}"The Tale of Jiraiya the Gallant."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a worthless story...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.\NThis tale is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Each chapter reads like one of\Nyour numerous legendary exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like an autobiography.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The main character of this book...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought his determination to\Nnever give up was really cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a lot like you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope my unborn child can become\N a ninja just like this main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I'd like your permission\Nto name my son after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a random name that\NI thought up while eating ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kushina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes...\NSo that makes me his godfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a great ninja who possesses\Nthe true talent of a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gave that child...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hokage that surpasses\Nall previous Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I never go back on my word...\NThat's my ninja way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it,\N {\i1}you are just like that {\i1}novel's main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've inherited Minato and\N{\i1}Kushina's wishes, their hopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a great ninja who\Npossesses the true talent of a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A ninja is one who endures,\None who stands brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me teach you one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important attribute\Nof a ninja is not the number of jutsu he masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the guts to never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never go back on your word\N{\i1}and never give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto, if that is your ninja way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then as your mentor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no business whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For everyone knows that a student\N{\i1}inherits his ninja way from his teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that so, Naruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fought his way back by sheer will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure his heart had stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the true choice\N{\i1}I was supposed to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite obstinate, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Message received!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A dying message...\NHe wrote it in code, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto... You are the child of prophecy,\N{\i1}I'm sure of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I entrust you with the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The frog...got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Tale of Jiraiya the Gallant"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it'll end a bit better I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final chapter will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Frog in the Well Drifts\N{\i1}Into the Great Ocean."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not bad... Not bad at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now... It's about time\N{\i1}I put down my pen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, that's right!\N{\i1}What should I name the sequel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Tale of Naruto Uzumaki."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... That has a nice ring to it...
